# Complete Portfolio Website - Ready for Deployment

## 🚀 Quick Deployment Guide

This package contains your complete portfolio website that you can deploy on any platform like Vercel, Netlify, Railway, or Render.

### Option 1: Deploy on Vercel (Recommended)
1. Upload this entire folder to GitHub
2. Connect your GitHub repo to Vercel
3. Vercel will automatically detect and deploy it
4. Your portfolio will be live in minutes!

### Option 2: Deploy on Netlify
1. Drag and drop this folder to Netlify
2. It will build and deploy automatically
3. Get your live URL instantly

### Option 3: Deploy on Railway/Render
1. Upload to GitHub
2. Connect to Railway or Render
3. Select Node.js as your runtime
4. It will deploy automatically

---

## 📁 What's Included

This package contains:
- Complete React frontend with TypeScript
- Express.js backend server
- All UI components (shadcn/ui)
- Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
- Resume download functionality
- Contact form
- Smooth scrolling navigation
- Professional portfolio layout

---

## 🔧 Local Development

To run locally:
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Visit: http://localhost:5000

---

## ✏️ Customization

To change content (names, contact info, etc.):
1. Edit `server/storage.ts`
2. Find the `defaultPortfolioData` object
3. Update any values you want to change
4. Save and redeploy

